These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, ferret
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, romance, scientific
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indian, indonesian
House: farmhouse, tower, victorian
1. the tower house is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the american##5
4. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the tower house##8
5. the farmhouse house is the indonesian##1
6. the tower house is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
7. the american is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
8. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the american##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Pet         | ferret  | fish    | chinchilla |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | romance  | animation  |
| Nationality   | indian     | american | indonesian |
| House     | tower     | victorian     | farmhouse        |

