.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, romance
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, soul
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, drawing, photography
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
2. the fan of d&b is between the person watching action movies and the fan of soul##2
3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
4. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
5. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
6. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre          | action | disaster     | romance  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | d&b       | soul    |
| Hobby   | photography    | chess | drawing |
| Transport     | bus     | airplane  | scooter |

