.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, salsa
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, bongani, prince
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, water-polo
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, collecting, hiking
1. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
4. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | d&b        | salsa      |
| Cigar   | prince   | bluemaster     | bongani  |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rugby      | water-polo |
| Hobby     | traveling  | hiking | collecting     |

