.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, dancing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra, dunhill
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, snowboarding
1. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the aristoff-smoker##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the pony##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Hobby           | video-games   | woodworking   | dancing     |
| Cigar   | aristoff | dunhill      | alhambra     |
| Pet           | bird        | ferret       | pony       |
| Sport         | rugby       | snowboarding | ice-hockey |

