.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, tiparillo, baccarat
City: boston, miami, new-york
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, indie, r&b
1. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
3. the baccarat-smoker is between the fan of indie and the bolivar-smoker##2
4. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Beverage      | 7up         | lemonade    | sprite  |
| Cigar          | bolivar      | baccarat      | tiparillo    |
| City         | miami | new-york | boston |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | electronic  | indie   |

