.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, hip-hop
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, roller
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, turtle
1. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the tram is the fan of gospel##1
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | juice      | coffee   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre           | house | gospel | hip-hop |
| Transport   | roller | tram | motorbike  |
| Pet           | turtle     | hamster  | goldfish |

