The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, sudoku
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, rose
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
2. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
3. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsrose is between the person driving the quad-bike and the owner of the hedgehog##2
6. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Pet          | fish    | goldfish  | hedgehog  |
| Hobby         | singing   | sudoku | puzzles    |
| Flower   | daffodil   | rose   | iris     |
| Transport     | quad-bike | car    | skateboard |

