2. the person who growsrose is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the accountant##7
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who likes emerald##6
5. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the fisherman##8
6. the paramedic is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
7. the person who likes brown is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
8. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |
| Color    | emerald     | fuchsia     | brown          |
| Flower   | tulip   | rose | amaryllis    |
| Job     | fisherman | paramedic  | accountant    |
| Sport   | rowing    | cricket    | skateboarding |

