3. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
4. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the person eating cranberry##7
5. the person eating cauliflower is the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
7. the person eating peas is the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
9. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
