.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-8-10::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, radish, spinach
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, ritmeester, fonseca
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, water-polo
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, apricot, grey
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
3. the person who likes apricot is not the person eating garlic##6
4. the person who likes grey is the person eating garlic##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who's sport is water-polo##7
7. the havana-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
8. the havana-smoker is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
9. the person who likes light-blue is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | garlic  | spinach  | radish     |
| Cigar   | fonseca | havana | ritmeester      |
| Sport         | cricket | tennis   | water-polo |
| Color     | grey   | apricot     | light-blue   |

