 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
 5. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
 9. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
10. the person eating mango is not the montecristo-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |    3     |
