3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, prince
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is the fan of indie##1
 3. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is not the fan of metal##6
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 7. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the dunhill-smoker##8
 8. the dunhill-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
 9. the fan of disco is between the dunhill-smoker and the person playing whist##2
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Game          | mah-jongg  | monopoly         | whist     |
